snippet.title: Snooker Basic Shots on Slow Motion - ShootersPool Billiards Simulation
snippet.description:
This is a video demonstration of the ShootersPool Billiards Simulation physics engine showing some snooker basic shots on slow motion.

Some of the shots that you can watch on the video are Back Spin, Top Spin, Drag Shot, Stun Shots, Side Spin, Top Right Spin, Swerve and Cue Ball Bouncing with the Cushions.

For recording this video, we have set a white cue ball with a black stripe in order to show you the cue ball behavior on the different snooker shots.

Hope you enjoy it snooker lovers 🙂.
